---
import Section from "./Section.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import HeroIlust from "../../assets/pics/hero.svg";
---

<Section id="home">
<div class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen text-center" id="hero">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 space-y-8">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            <span class="block">アイデアを、</span>
            <span class="block">画面の中から</span>
            <span class="block">現実の世界へ</span>
        </h1>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <p class="font-medium">課題にお悩みですか？</p>
            <p>AI・IoTソリューションで、製造業・物流・農業・医療・小売業界の<br>DX推進を支援します。</p>
            <p>PoCから本格実装まで、ワンストップで開発します。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center pt-8">
            <a href="#contact" class="px-10 py-5 bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 rounded-2xl text-center text-white text-xl font-semibold transition-colors duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
                無料相談申し込み (30分)
            </a>
            <a href="#pricing" class="px-10 py-5 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl text-center text-blue-500 border-2 border-blue-500 text-xl font-semibold transition-colors duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
                料金体系を見る
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</Section>